{"tid":1864771,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"給香港人的守護天使","createTime":"2020-02-05T19:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T13:12:29.000Z","uid":133383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eded8da4cb39de6d672c64e25a11c42b50ff4139","tid":1864771,"uid":133383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T19:19:47.000Z","msg":"無論在醫院裡救急扶危 抗疫救災 又或者站在街外為全香港市民爭取公眾利益時 <br />\n你們總是勇敢 無悔地站在最前 為市民傘風擋雨 押上自身前途 甚至捨身成仁<br />\n辛苦晒你地 無以為報 只好講一聲「多謝」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />❤❤❤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">幾十歲入都係第一次寫 自己睇到都覺「骨痺」既野，所以深夜發帖，但完全發自真心</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd51217effba4e1cc2930d9d43e90f15753d4bb","tid":1864771,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"天使<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929c4bdfc7d6981fc202111f5f743877bb69aefd","tid":1864771,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fbb1706eb8545577388706962cb6c3f05454a9b","tid":1864771,"uid":281417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"醫護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}